title: Bill Burr: A Joke about McDonald's
description: Bill Burr jokes about McDonald's in his Netflix special, "Walk Your Way Out". Grab your tickets at NetflixIsAJokeFest.com to see Bill and your other favorite comedians in the Netflix is a Joke Fest happening April 28th-May 8th in Los Angeles.
